{
  "page": "Grief",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the bay, see <a href=\"/index.php/Gulf_of_Grief\" title=\"Gulf of Grief\">Gulf of Grief</a>.</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Grief.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c6/Grief.jpg/350px-Grief.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"229\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/c/c6/Grief.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Grief.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><i>Grief</i> by David Auden Nash © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><i><b>Grief</b></i> is an <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> longship and part of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Iron Fleet\">Iron Fleet</a>. Her captain is <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Sparr\" title=\"Rodrik Sparr\">Rodrik Sparr</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Crew\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Crew</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grief&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><i>Grief</i> has black sails.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grief&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grief&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>Grief</i> is among the ships that make the voyage to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot_on_Old_Wyk\" title=\"Kingsmoot on Old Wyk\">kingsmoot on Old Wyk</a>. During the kingsmoot, Lord Captain <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a> orders <i>Grief</i> and <i><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Vengeance\" title=\"Iron Vengeance\">Iron Vengeance</a></i> to lie between <i><a href=\"/index.php/Silence\" title=\"Silence\">Silence</a></i> and the open sea.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_the_Shields\" title=\"Taking of the Shields\">taking of the Shields</a>, Lord Victarion keeps <i>Grief</i>, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Dagon\" title=\"Lord Dagon\">Lord Dagon</a></i>, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Wind\" title=\"Iron Wind\">Iron Wind</a></i>, and <i><a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Bane\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Bane\">Maiden's Bane</a></i> as part of his rearguard, commanding from his own ship, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Victory\" title=\"Iron Victory\">Iron Victory</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grief&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>Grief</i> is the fifty-fourth and last ironborn ship to arrive at the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Cedars\" title=\"Isle of Cedars\">Isle of Cedars</a> while the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Iron Fleet\">Iron Fleet</a> regroups on their way to <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a>. The crew has rescued <a href=\"/index.php/Moqorro\" title=\"Moqorro\">Moqorro</a> from the water, and <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Sparr\" title=\"Rodrik Sparr\">the Vole</a> presents the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_priest\" title=\"Red priest\">red priest</a> to Victarion on <i>Iron Victory</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Crew\">Crew</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grief&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Crew\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Sparr\" title=\"Rodrik Sparr\">Rodrik Sparr</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grief&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, The Iron Suitor.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, The Iron Captain.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_29\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 29\">Chapter 29</a>, The Reaver.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403110941\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.044 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.072 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 570/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8770/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2107/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 110/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2002/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.64 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   53.139      1 -total\n 57.76%   30.691      1 Template:Italic_title\n 23.43%   12.448      5 Template:Ref\n 15.97%    8.487      5 Template:Ref/core\n 11.45%    6.086      1 Template:For\n  6.12%    3.253      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awo